  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK476">
<l>nuṉikkompa rēṟiṉā raḵtiṟan tūkki </l>
<l>ṉuyirkkiṟuti yāki viṭum</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>There will be an end to the life of him who, having climbed out to the end of a branch, ventures to go further.</l>
            </lg>
